        <title>Hugo搭建个人博客</title>
        <link>https://baichuan-sihai.github.io/hugo/p/hugo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</link>
